<help battle hit>

If there is nothing hindering you, you can start a fight in this way.
There are many other ways to find yourself in battle, including many
of the more offensive skills and spells.

Syntax:  hit <<i_th> [target]
Syntax:  kill <<i_th> [target]

Example:  hit priest	Attempts to start a fight with the priest.
Example:  kill priest   Does the same.

<color = blue>
See Also:  abilities, assist
</color></help>
